frontend.dialog

Class PersonalDetailsDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • frontend.dialog.PersonalDetailsDialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class PersonalDetailsDialog
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Creates the layout to be used by the add and edit JOptionPanes opened from the Management menu. This layout contains various text fields which the user can use to either add a new patient or modify an exisiting one.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alessandro
